item.description:
Betaflight 3.3 Release will be ready for March 1st. New feature : Arming disabled while connected to Betaflight configurator Arming is now disabled when the flight controller is connected to the Betaflight configurator.
This was added in order to keep users from accidentally arming their craft when testing their RX / mode switches with a battery connected.
In order to enable arming for bench testing, go to the &lsquo;Motors&rsquo; tab and enable the &lsquo;Motor test mode&rsquo; switch (REMOVE ALL PROPELLERS FIRST);
